HEADWORD: Confinable
<hw>Con*fin"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Capable of being
confined, restricted, or limited.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

